

Declaration
-----------

This is the demo of Imagems, a mind game, where it is your task to solve
given patterns of differents elements (solid blocks, balls, cubes).

Imagems offers you 99 mindblowing levels. 5 of them are playable in this
demo.

There are own passwords and saveable hiscore-tables for each level.


You can purchase Imagems for

		DM 45.- with packing
	     or DM 40.- WITHOUT packing

under following address:


			Brainwave Entertainment
			Lindenstr. 8
			D-71540 Murrhardt
			GERMANY
